%2F1508057435505.png&h=f091cd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由此可見，肥鳩大隻同本癲狗實力縣殊，想借本癲狗上位卻慘敗收場，因而只能作出零星而無力的反抗，反過來誣衊本癲狗借佢條傻鳩上位，其實本癲狗只係從容撚狗，已獲得大家支持</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>同時亦證明左，無論肥鳩大隻花盡心機，唸盡辦法想同本癲狗玩，但換黎既結果只有慘敗同被撚，所以永遠活係本癲狗既陰影之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d1a746e43fc1c2038d65ee3dcf067e302be33573","tid":561412,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"阻我收爐者，大師兄斬撚死你！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f905a18175245b96a76f36c3a2b5f53e361709","tid":561412,"uid":74981,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:00:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>文盲肥絲大隻平時扮有學識，經常借challenge人打錯字上位，點知自己卻俾人捉番文盲唔識字兼打錯字，慘被撚到笠水，廢物現形實錄</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">(一)<br />\n原來巴塞已經發明左用聲控黎剎車同踩油</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/546777/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/546777/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>(二)<br />\n肥絲大隻分右手未？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/538769/1?ref=android&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/538769/1?ref=android&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>想靠大家上位又上唔到仲俾人撚番轉頭咪你哩種廢柴囉</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330fbc4818ef67065db9978214bfffb252c3cfdd","tid":561412,"uid":74981,"like":0,"